<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:28.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Ultrases barlagy (&nbsp;<b>ultrases&nbsp;</b>) bagry&#328;
&yacute;agda&yacute;yny g&ouml;rkezer, pankreatit &yacute;a-da a&#351;gazan
asty m&auml;zini&#328; d&uuml;wn&uuml;k keselini kesgitl&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:28.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Ultrases&nbsp;<b>barlagyny&nbsp;</b>ge&ccedil;irip bolma&yacute;an
&yacute;a-da maglumat &yacute;eterlik bolmadyk
&yacute;agda&yacute;ynda&nbsp;hasaplanan tomografi&yacute;a (&nbsp;<b>KT&nbsp;</b>)
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;I&ccedil;ege i&ccedil;egesini&#328; bozulmalaryny we
bagry&#328; da&#351;yndaky kanallarda bozulmalary&#328; bardygyny
kesgitl&auml;&#328;.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:28.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Magnit-rezonans holangiopankreatografi&yacute;a (&nbsp;<b>MRCP&nbsp;</b>),
i&ccedil;ege we da&#351;arky &ouml;t &yacute;ollaryny &#351;ekillendirmek
&uuml;&ccedil;in takyk we ygtybarly usuldyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:28.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
