</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Portal damarda basy&#351;y&#328; &yacute;okarlanmagy (&nbsp;<b>portal
gipertoni&yacute;a&nbsp;</b>) - i&yacute;mit si&#328;diri&#351; ulgamyndan gan
portal damary arkaly bagry&#328; i&ccedil;ine gir&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Siroz,
damar arkaly adaty gan akmagyny b&ouml;kde&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Toksinler
bagyrda s&uuml;z&uuml;lme&yacute;&auml;r we ganda gal&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:28.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
