</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>D&uuml;w&uuml;rtigi&#328;, a&#351;gazany&#328;, gemorroidal
damarlary&#328; gi&#328;elmegi (&nbsp;<b>varikoz damarlary&nbsp;</b>).&nbsp;Portal
damardan gan akmagy ha&yacute;allanda &yacute;a-da petiklenende, gan
be&yacute;leki organlara (a&#351;gazan, gyzyl&ouml;dege) ga&yacute;dyp
gel&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Pressureokarlanan basy&#351; damarlardan
&yacute;arylyp, gan akyp biler.&nbsp;Gemorro&yacute;dan &yacute;okarky
a&#351;gazanda &yacute;a-da &ouml;zofagusda gan akma, derrew lukman&ccedil;ylyk
k&ouml;megini talap ed&yacute;&auml;n durmu&#351; &uuml;&ccedil;in howply
&yacute;agda&yacute;.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:28.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
